reviewText:
Funny presented cartoon explicitly satirizes clergy of whose belonging to Vatican can hardly be misunderstood.

According to preambles opening every chart, this ten episode set was created by a pupil bored at lessons conducted by a priest entertaining his students while teaching eternal ethics and moral issues, as supposed, one could understand, with just established government-funded clergy positions at schools round Australia.

It is interesting both an animation and DVD were produced before such an educative motion in Australia.
